		{"id":"92616385b3e8f666","type":"text","text":"# Battle\n## Challenge\nCrystal Ball that has a magical storm inside it with a radius that does 1d8 slashing damage when someone enters in to it or starts their turn there. As long as it is active, it will attract Pearlspawn at a doubling rate every round (1, 2, 4, 8, ect) Any ranged attack will be blown away.\n\n## Enemies\n[[Stormcaller Cultist]]\n[[Stormcaller Knight]]\n[[Stormcaller Cultist Fanatic]]\n### Add ons\n[[Campaigns/The Anchor’s Secret/Enemies/Pearlbound|Pearlbound]]","x":1880,"y":-260,"width":487,"height":476},
		{"id":"b663aa049c5e324b","type":"text","text":"# Find Fishing buddy","x":907,"y":360,"width":250,"height":86},
		{"id":"e3c36686afb02312","type":"text","text":"# As a Priest of Miraine. He is the only one who can move the pearl.","x":682,"y":623,"width":475,"height":117},
		{"id":"8f01e34d8960f51d","type":"file","file":"World/Factions/The Verdant Strand/Tidecutters.md","x":665,"y":960,"width":400,"height":400},
